{"data":[{"id":563762157,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":307595822,"title":"高中生对哥德巴赫猜想的证明有哪些错误？","question_type":"normal","created":1546272354,"updated_time":1546301579,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563762157","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-943eef380d8d25dd4cfc1b50bd00016e_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546273883,"updated_time":1546275531,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":28,"comment_count":11,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e用你家门钥匙能开马云家的门吗？他家可能连锁眼都没好吗！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e小朋友的思路就农民伯伯想象“皇帝一定扛金锄头”这样吧，不是错不错的问题，是他的思维和真正在解这个问题的人完全不在一个维度上，他无法去想象这个问题到底意味着什么，甚至他都无法摸到通往这个问题的门在哪，连该用什么工具来解决问题都不知道。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e他的问题甚至不在证明有没有错，而在从一开始就连哥德巴赫猜想要证明什么都理解错了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e至于具体的问题……从负质数和2n+1开始就让人瞠目结舌了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e只能说，凡伟还知道看看大物再说话呢，高中生有梦想是好事，严肃对待梦想就更值得钦佩了，如果能选择相关专业进一步学习就太好了，但无边无际地做梦就是他自己不对了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-2a0c706f1841a91cb623c7dab4b6cec9_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"226\" data-rawheight=\"140\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-2a0c706f1841a91cb623c7dab4b6cec9_b.jpg\" class=\"content_image\" width=\"226\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='226'%20height='140'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"226\" data-rawheight=\"140\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-2a0c706f1841a91cb623c7dab4b6cec9_b.jpg\" class=\"content_image lazy\" width=\"226\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-2a0c706f1841a91cb623c7dab4b6cec9_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e就，朋友说他是营销号，我觉得真的不是，就是个爱做梦的高中生。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e他只是很严肃地用自己有限的知识试图解决这个问题，很遗憾的是，虽然不该嘲笑他，但真的有点好笑_(:з」∠)_\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003ca data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/306537777/answer/560489102\" class=\"internal\"\u003e如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？\u003c/a\u003e\u003cp\u003e说实话他可以看看这个回答感受一下什么叫思维方式的差距。\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"用你家门钥匙能开马云家的门吗？他家可能连锁眼都没好吗！小朋友的思路就农民伯伯想象“皇帝一定扛金锄头”这样吧，不是错不错的问题，是他的思维和真正在解这个问题的人完全不在一个维度上，他无法去想象这个问题到底意味着什么，甚至他都无法摸到通往这个…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ce